    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can move, cast a spell, and move again before foes react.<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Key ability score 15, Dex 15, Mobility, caster level 4th.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: As a full action, you can move up to your speed and cast a single spell with a casting time of one standard action or less at any point during your movement. If you have a supernatural ability that can be activated as a standard action or less, you can instead use that ability at any point during your movement.<br><br><strong>Normal</strong>: You can move only before or after casting a spell, not both.</span></p>",
